## 📦 Installation & Environments

**Standard Build**:
```bash
pip install mlplt
```

**Full AI Build (Recommended)**:
```bash
pip install mlplt[full]
```

**Google Colab Setup**:
```python
import mlpilot as ml
ml.colab_setup() # Automatically configures local AI backends for 100% reliability
```

